{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"1":"Purification (Kitab Al-Taharah)"}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":389,"arabicnumber":389,"text":"حدثنا موسى بن إسماعيل، حدثنا حماد، أخبرنا ثابت البناني، عن أبي نضرة، قال بزق رسول الله صلى الله عليه وسلم في ثوبه وحك بعضه ببعض ‏.‏","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih Lighairihi"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih"}],"reference":{"book":1,"hadith":389}}]}